content:
Iqbar Ali-Abdula is the name of the famed bug hunter and researcher that first studied the Kalphite species in the Kharidian Desert. Apparently, this research drove him insane, causing him to run into the desert, screaming. Whether he is still alive is unknown but it is hinted that he is the Weird Old Man outside the Kalphite Hive.

Iqbar is mentioned only in the Varrock Museum, in the display that discusses the Kalphite Queen.
rawContent:
'''Iqbar Ali-Abdula''' is the name of the famed bug hunter and researcher that first studied the [[Kalphite]] species in the [[Kharidian Desert]]. Apparently, this research drove him insane, causing him to run into the desert, screaming. Whether he is still alive is unknown but it is hinted that he is the [[Weird Old Man]] outside the [[Kalphite Hive]].

Iqbar is mentioned only in the [[Varrock Museum]], in the display that discusses the [[Kalphite Queen]].
